\id 3JN - Nooni 
\h 3 Jon 
\toc1 3 Jon 
\toc2 3Jon 
\toc3 3Jon 
\mt2 Ŋwa' wvu bokaŋ botɛte wvu 
\mt1 Jon 
\imt1 Fiɛɛ fì nu ɛ̂ Ŋwa' Jon wvu bokaŋ botɛte wvun e 
\ip Jon wvù teŋe ɛkolɛ kew lɛ cee ɛkolɛ ke kentaashɛ ke bonyii bo mbee le, to saŋ ŋwa' we wvu bokaŋ botɛte wvun fô wee mvu wvu fwe ɛ̂ kentaashɛ ke bonyii bo mbee le ɛ diee nu Gayus. Wvú nu ɛ saŋ ɛ bɛnse Gayus yî nfi wvù wvú nyaa ɛ̂ bonyii bo mbee le. Wvú nu ɛ tefe tɛn Gayus lɛ wvú eyɛnè ɛkumɛ wee mvu wvù bó to teŋe lɛ Diotefɛs njefo wvú to tune keeyuw diɛw ye le. 
\is1 Bikuu bi mwɛɛm e ɛ̂ Ŋwa' wvun e 
\io1 1-4 Keŋkɛwcɛ 
\io1 5-8 Ɛ Jon bɛnse Gayus 
\io1 9-10 Ɛ Jon lom gee di Diotefɛs e 
\io1 11-12 Ɛ Jon bɛnse gee di Dɛmitiyus e 
\io1 13-15 Kemɛse 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 2Jon 1\x*Ɛ̀ nu me wvù cee ɛkolɛ kentaashɛ ke bonyii bo mbee le. Me nsaaŋke ŋwa' wvun fô wo le Gayus wvù nsaa yɛm shém. Me ŋkooŋke naa wo yî kecɛɛy e. 
\s1 Ɛ Jon bɛnse Gayus 
\p  
\v 2 Nsaa yɛm shém, me mbunlee lɛ mwɛɛm mvunciim egɛne ntay ɛ̂ keba kuw e, ɛ wo tɛmyi yî nyam ye le kɛ no me ŋkee lɛ wo tɛmyi ɛ̂ keyoy e.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 2Jon 4\x*Me nto nu ɛ n'yuw njoŋ baay no boom bo bwee wesebeene le bomew to fɛsɛɛ jan see ɛkumɛ no wo leeme yî kecɛɛy e bô fitele fiuw ficii. Ɛ ɛ̀ nu naa kecɛɛy lɛ wo bii kecɛɛy e.  
\v 4 Kɛ fiɛɛ fimew bvuu nu dvú fì nulo ege ɛ́ me en'yuuke njoŋ nfele keen'yuuke lɛ boom bobem bii kecɛɛy e kɛ. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Ibu 13:2\x*Nsaa yɛm shém, lemme dì wo lemte fô boom bo bwee wesebeene le, ɛfey mvunciim fô bò nu botolo le, nu ɛ wo lemte naa lɛŋ.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Tay 3:13\x*Bó to nu ɛ see ɛ̂ kentaashɛ ke bonyii bo mbee le ke jan ɛkumɛ keŋkoŋɛn kuw. Ɛ̀ momtè kɛ fici boba bonyii ɛ̂ je yì Nyo' shieele le nonɛn yî lɛne dibole.  
\v 7 Ɛ̀ keè lɛ bó buy ɛkfuŋ ɛ ɛ̀ nu nje diee di Klistu le, ɛ bó baa etaale nfi mvu ɛ̂ bonyii bò yaa nu bo Nyo' le kɛ.  
\v 8 Nonɛn, beene kɛŋke keetomtè boba bonyii, wvu lɛ beene ɛ bó enù bonyii bò lemte yî fiɛɛ le fimwaaŋ ɛkumɛ kecɛɛy. 
\s1 Ɛkumɛ Diotefɛs bô Dɛmitiyus 
\p  
\v 9 Me nto nu ɛ nsaŋ fiɛɛ fô kentaashɛ ke bonyii bo mbee le kenɛn e, geenɛn ɛ Diotefɛs wvù kooŋke keelewse ɛkolɛ kew fwe, faŋɛ yaa eyuw wee wvù ɛ̀ nu me le kɛ.  
\v 10 Nonɛn, me nu ŋke endioo ɛ nto, ɛ́ me enjike fiɛɛ fì wvú gee fin fokuse, no wvú ghane kunsene mvuŋkunsɛn, jemyi díɛw yì befe ɛkumɛ me. No wvú gee nonɛn, wvú baa cim ffuu bô fifiɛ kɛ. Wvú tune tɛn keefiisene boom bo bwee wesebeene le, tune tɛn fo bonyii bò gomte keefiisene bó efiisenè. Ɛ́ bó dioo gomte keefiisɛn, ɛ́ wvú mum kuŋ lo bó ɛ̂ kentaashɛ ke bonyii bo mbee le ɛnte. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt 1Jon 2:29\x*Nsaa yɛm shém, fo wo ebeŋenè fiɛɛ fì befe kɛ. Ɛ̀ beŋenè ɛ ɛ̀ nu fì jee. Wee wvù gee fiɛɛ fì jee nu wee Nyo', ɛ wvù gee fì befe nu ɛ wvú baa kee wase Nyo' kɛ.  
\v 12 Dɛmitiyus nu fiew wee ɛ bonyii bocii jemyi mwɛɛm mvù jee ɛkumɛ wvú, ɛ keŋge kew kè jee jemyi tɛn ɛkumɛ wvú. Bese tɛn jemyi ɛkumɛ wvú. Ɛ wo kee lo lɛ fiɛɛ fì bese jemyi ɛkumɛ wvú nu kecɛɛy. 
\s1 Ŋgayma 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 2Jon 12\x*Me mbɛɛ ŋkɛŋke mwɛɛm nteen keensaŋ ɛ̂ wo, geenɛn kɛ me ŋkooŋke keensaŋ lo bô ɛte ke ŋwa' le kɛ.  
\v 14 Me n'yɛne lɛ ɛ̀ shɛke caan ɛ́ me ento en'yɛn lo wo le, ɛ́ bee wo ejemyi ɛ wee yɛne wee le ɛ̂ jise. 
\p  
\v 15 Nyɛkeey enù fô wo le. Nsáa yesebeewo gayte wo le. Gayɛ nsáa yesebeewo le yicii wee mwaaŋ mwaaŋ bó le, enya ɛ̂ me.